  "description": "Box-drawing and block-element characters (U+2500–U+259F) added to the picker database. Names follow a systematic '\u003cposition\u003e [style] border' scheme so queries like 'top left double border' or 'bottom border round' hit exactly one glyph. The packer and the Go loader append 'box ascii art' keywords to every entry and rank box art below emojis in general searches; the 'b:' query prefix filters to these entries only. The rarely used mixed single/double forms (U+2552–U+256C subset) are intentionally omitted.",
